data.description: Location, Location,Location!!!, Move in ready, 4 bedrooms, 2 1/2- bathroom, colonial located in the top rated Appoquinimink School District.  2 car attached side entry garage, full basement, a spacious family room with wood burning fireplace, finished walk out basement, backs to woods. This home is conveniently located in the heart of Middletown, walking/biking distance to Silver Lake Elementary School & Park, Everett Meredith Middle School, Appoquinimink Public Library, Shopping & newly constructed state of the art Middletown YMCA.  This well-maintained home features newer roof installed 04/2020, HVAC installed 08/2022 with a transferable warranty, gutter guards, & wood burning fireplace liner replaced 2023. A must see.
